summary:
### Exploration Results Summary:  
- **High-grade gold-silver trenching results** confirmed at Cerro Verde prospect, Dynasty Gold Project:  
  - 4.5m @ **3.2 g/t Au, 3.5 g/t Ag** (CVC25-122)  
  - 6.2m @ **2.0 g/t Au, 20.2 g/t Ag** (CVC25-104)  
  - 6.4m @ **2.3 g/t Au, 12.1 g/t Ag** (CVT25-009)  
  - 12.0m @ **0.8 g/t Au, 4.7 g/t Ag** (CVT25-011, extensional zone)  
- **Resource drilling ongoing**: Two diamond rigs active; 6,000m program to support JORC resource update by late Q3 2025.  
- **Exploration progress**: Mobile magneto-telluric (MMT) survey completed; results expected in 3–4 weeks.  

**No material capital markets or trading-specific information (e.g., capital raising, halts) identified.**  

*(Note: Omitted operational/JORC details as per guidelines.)*
